Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.31,0:02:00.89,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}La Going Merry è rimasta ancorata su un'isola deserta per \Nquattro giorni così che Luffy e Robin potessero riprendersi.{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:00.89,0:02:05.85,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dopodiché, siamo ripartiti. Oggi è la terza mattina\Nda quando abbiamo ripreso la navigazione.{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:05.85,0:02:08.69,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,Il cielo è sereno e il clima è primaverile!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:09.61,0:02:11.31,Thoughts-207+,,0,0,0,,A tratti anche estivo.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:16.70,0:02:18.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che bella giornata!{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:19.09,0:02:22.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Nami cara!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.60,0:02:30.29,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ho preparato del {\i1}pomme paille{\i0}. \N{\i1}Mademoiselle{\i0}, se gradisce, ne prenda pure.
Comment: 5,0:02:25.60,0:02:30.29,Note-207+,,0,0,0,,pomme paille: shoe string potatoes
Dialogue: 5,0:02:32.42,0:02:34.10,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oh, che buono!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:34.10,0:02:36.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che gioia!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.68,0:02:39.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sta' zitto, deficiente! \NNon riesco a dormire così.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:39.47,0:02:43.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì, sì, scusami, cactus.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:43.00,0:02:45.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cos'hai detto, sopracciglia a mirino?! Eh?!{Kinda -Cora}{yeah, very kinda... ma non penso lo userà molto quindi ok}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.95,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Be– Cos'hai detto, bastardo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:47.95,0:02:50.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sopracciglia a mirino.{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:02:53.64,0:02:57.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Luffy! Vai! Luffy! Bene!\N– Luffy! Vai! Luffy! Bene!
Dialogue: 5,0:02:57.61,0:03:02.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Luffy! Vai! Luffy!\N– Luffy! Vai! Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:04.43,0:03:06.98,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ti stavamo aspettando!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:05.64,0:03:06.98,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:13.79,0:03:16.75,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,La mia imitazione di quando ero congelato!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:23.72,0:03:27.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Uff... Hai proprio del coraggio a fare così \Nquando sei quasi morto congelato.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:29.74,0:03:30.73,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ero simile?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:30.73,0:03:33.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eri uguale! Uguale, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:33.48,0:03:35.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vedi di pulire come si deve, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:35.87,0:03:38.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,O-Oh, Nami! Che stai mangiando?
Dialogue: 5,0:03:38.86,0:03:41.14,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Paille{\i0}! Sono patate.
Dialogue: 5,0:03:41.94,0:03:45.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Patate? Anch'io ho fame! Ehi, Sanji!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:45.24,0:03:48.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Quanto devi dormire ancora per essere contento?!
Dialogue: 5,0:03:48.96,0:03:52.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Quanto dormo sono affari miei! \NSe ne ho voglia, lo faccio!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:03.59,0:04:06.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ha detto che si chiama {\i1}paille{\i0}! Proprio buono!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:06.30,0:04:08.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cos'è un "{\i1}paille{\i0}"?
Dialogue: 5,0:04:08.58,0:04:12.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È carne di coda del grande mostro Paille.{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:12.65,0:04:16.19,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sono stato io ad abbatterlo! Era lungo cento metri!{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,"Cento metri"?! Sei fantastico, Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.46,0:04:21.61,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Figurati, uno così me lo mangio a colazione!{Cora}{esempio di frase a cui  il \N non serve. evviva il 16:9}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Eh? Ti sei svegliato presto per mangiarlo quindi?{-Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:24.26,0:04:27.49,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Chopper, prova a dire il mio nome.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:27.49,0:04:31.08,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh? O-Ovviamente è... C-Captain...
Dialogue: 5,0:04:31.08,0:04:35.58,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Esatto! Il mio nome è Captain... Usopp!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:37.42,0:04:39.34,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.50,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Oooh! Mia dolce Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.72,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:43.72,0:04:46.51,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Come ti senti? Hai qualche brivido di freddo?{sono tornata ad una versione precedente di Cora perché quella di Dave aveva perso il senso dei brividi. avere freddo e avere i brividi di freddo è diverso. uno ha freddo quando è freddo, i brividi li hai se stai male}
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.51,0:04:50.97,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, grazie a te mi sento piuttosto bene. \NTi ringrazio, signor medico di bordo!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:50.97,0:04:56.60,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ah... Chiamarmi "medico di bordo" \Nnon mi rende per niente felice, maledetta~!
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.60,0:04:58.44,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A me sembra felice.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:57.56,0:04:58.44,Secondary-207+,,0,0,0,,Già.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.27,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Non sforzarti, Robin.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:00.27,0:05:05.17,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}So che vedere Luffy così energico dopo aver \Npassato lo stesso potrebbe farti sentire in difetto,{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:05.17,0:05:07.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,ma riposati pure con calma un altro po'.{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:07.16,0:05:09.16,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Yay!\N– Non ti so facendo complimenti!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:09.73,0:05:13.23,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Robin cara! \NVuoi che ti prepari qualcosa di caldo?{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:13.23,0:05:14.54,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Hai fame?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:15.38,0:05:16.21,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Allora...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.22,0:05:18.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,posso avere un caffè?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:18.30,0:05:21.03,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Certo, con piacere!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.69,0:05:36.85,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.56,0:05:38.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cos'è quello?
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.07,0:05:50.26,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Questo {\i1}paille{\i0} è così buono che \Nnon riesco a smettere di mangiarlo!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.26,0:05:52.00,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sì! È buonissimo!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:52.00,0:05:54.04,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ehi, non potremmo venderlo per guadagnarci?{Cora}{sempre cps comunque}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:54.04,0:05:55.37,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, Luffy!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:55.37,0:05:58.30,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,U-U-Una rana sta nuotando a stile libero!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:58.30,0:05:59.46,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cosa?!
Dialogue: 5,0:05:59.46,0:06:01.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Sta venendo lì, guardate!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.48,0:06:02.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Davvero?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Una rana? {\i1}Quella{\i0} rana?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:04.38,0:06:09.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Ehi, Luffy! Stai davvero prendendo sul \Nserio quello che dice il re degli stupidi?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.47,0:06:11.55,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Dopotutto, una rana non può nuotare a stile lib–!{Cora}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:11.55,0:06:14.31,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Lo sta facendo! \NLa rana sta nuotando a stile libero!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:14.31,0:06:16.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Seguiamola, uomini!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.15,0:06:16.99,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:16.99,0:06:20.80,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Spiegate le vele! Prendete i remi! \NGirate lo scafo a ore due!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:20.80,0:06:21.86,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– Sì!\N– Sì!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:21.86,0:06:22.89,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Veloci!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:22.89,0:06:26.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Non so perché, ma sento che dobbiamo seguirla!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:27.04,0:06:29.28,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Scusate l'attesa, {\i1}mademoiselle{\i0}.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:31.64,0:06:32.83,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che succede?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:32.83,0:06:34.70,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Cosa? Cos'è successo?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.80,0:06:39.96,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Pare che la nave abbia cambiato rotta.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:39.96,0:06:44.42,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Ehi, voi! Perché avete cambiato rotta per conto vostro?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.65,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,A proposito, ascolta, Nami!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:46.65,0:06:49.38,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,{\q2}Abbiamo trovato una rana enorme piena di ferite!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.10,0:06:51.68,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Che vuoi dire?
Dialogue: 5,0:06:51.68,0:06:55.24,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Vogliamo farla arrosto e mangiarla!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.24,0:06:56.47,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,– La vuoi mangiare?!\N– La vuoi mangiare?!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:57.89,0:06:59.25,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,È vero!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.30,0:07:02.48,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Eh? È un faro quello?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.60,0:07:08.15,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,Perché c'è un faro in un posto come quello? \NChe ci sia qualcuno?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.53,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,C-Che succede? Hai visto un'isola?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:10.53,0:07:14.87,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,No, c'è un faro. \NPerò non è il posto indicato dal Log Pose.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:14.87,0:07:17.79,Main-207+,,0,0,0,,E la rana? Guidaci verso la rana!
